---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
import { SITE } from "../site-config";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="sr-only">
      Hi, I'm {SITE.author.firstName}, a full stack software developer (frontend-focused) from {SITE.location.countryName}. My primary
      tools of choice includes: JavaScript, React, Solidjs, Astro, Svelte,
      Nodejs. I also have knowledge of SEO and design. Beyond coding, I'm passionate about design, illustration,
      animation and 3D modelling and traveling. An unusual hobby of mine is
      collecting vintage passports, they're interesting pieces of history to me.
      While I have some preferred tools, I always choose the best one for the
      job, even if it's not on my usual list. My goal is to find the right
      solution for each project.
    </p>
    <div aria-hidden="true" class="text-sm font-light">
      <p class="text-sm font-light">
        Hi, I'm {SITE.author.firstName}, a full stack software developer (frontend-focused) from {SITE.location.countryName}.
      </p>
      <br />
      My primary tools of choice includes:
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>JavaScript</li>
        <li>React</li>
        <li>Solidjs</li>
        <li>Astro</li>
        <li>Svelte</li>
        <li>Nodejs</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm font-light mt-2">
        I also have knowledge of SEO and UX/UI.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      Beyond coding, I'm passionate about design, illustration, animation and 3D
      modelling and traveling. An unusual hobby of mine is collecting vintage
      passports, they're interesting pieces of history to me.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
